Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The editor rejected everything again...\N"Those manuscripts are poor even as a fiction" huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, I was hoping to see your style improving, \Nbut you don't seem to even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, with this interview...\NYou give me another chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you assure me this one \Nwon't become another manuscript I reject?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll be fired soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't editor being too harsh on Ginya today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With his attitude, this is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The name is Oumi Shunichi. Be aware, \Nthe person bearing this name is unique in a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.88,Song,,0,0,10,,Oumi Main Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He postulates pachislot machines alive? \N Alive, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,20,,{\fade(700,800)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1.3\blur1.5\3c&H779358&\4c&H3A5C36&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\fscx114\fscy92\3a&H4A&}Episode 3 \N {\fs86}Palpation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Doctor! Young Doctor, \Nwould you like to dine with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He has already promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go driving instead? \NCome on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Doctor, we still should drink together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor! You are so unreliable...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine. One at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. We should get back to work. \NCome on. On our ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi, the chief physician is ready to see you.\NPlease wait at his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he is a spoiled person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait for him on that sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A chief physician a pachislot player?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I arranged an interview with you.\NTurning Gears' reporter Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Turning Gears?" \NFrankly speaking, never heard of such a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a small magazine, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no problem. If my next dissertation \Nis of your interest, it's my pleasure to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magazine is bound to grow big this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissertation...\NHave you already composed its plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you read the dissertation summary \Nprior to the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I happen to see some of your ideas \Nas extremely unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All accepted by public nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Should this mean such ideas \Nare recognized warmly in medical society too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I mean... You got me here.\NThis, of course! This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Massage with fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Massage... Is not precisely the thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow it feels like \Nwe're not on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in. Apologies. I made you wait. \NWeren't you looking for me, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shunichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot!? Shunichi! Is this how you waste your time \Nwhen not courting nurses!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not over yet! \NHey! Shunichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping he'd be away past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just hoping to interview you, \Nneither is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's do it in my mansion.\NIt's just two or three minutes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If my AWOL is discovered, we'd have trouble. \NLet's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you seem to be terribly popular here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This popularity is just a consequence \Nof being heir to the hospital. Bothersome at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Only women like my mother appeal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, grandpa is still lively. \NMeaning that I'm not getting any peace soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'd like to be mistaken on the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long have you been playing pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eight years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it was when you were 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. \NHurry up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Thanks for the hospitality. \NCan we finally begin the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, before that, \NI want to show you this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. \NCome, come. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Such an extensive collection \Nis not to be seen every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing. \NIt still lacks a lot of cool machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm checking her current condition.\NShe's a child, particularly capricious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A child?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They are children, living beings. \NWhen playing, one should consider their condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take their mood into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, pachislot are alive. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not someone's pet robot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for once, can agree with one thing - the better you treat your surroundings, the better it performs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The same goes for pachislot. \NThe way you touch the buttons defines the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's in a good mood now.\NYou should try and hear it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear it already?\NThis kid's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \NNothing but reels spinning motor reaches my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by throwing away the bias \Nof soulless pachislot machines, you can hear their pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sole way to understand a child's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, the only way to ensure hitting Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to prove your certainty \Nby hitting Big right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't this machine be simply out of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not. Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is perturbating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just never mind it \Nand begin the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, girl.\NI expect a fine combo from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is too shy to let me win in front of you.\NYes, yes! This was the case all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure likes his bets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have made up with Ginya \Nand hold no grudges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried \Nhe did not show up neither yesterday nor today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot, isn't it? \NIt's more important to him than keeping a promise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of writing the manuscript \Nthat won't be rejected that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is preoccupied with a Pachislot article, \Ncould he unconsciously get fully engaged again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it should be no less than a column.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The last matter I'd like to know.\NTo you, Oumi, what does pachislot stand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally to me, pachislot \Nis a living being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be your gentle lover \Nor a shrewd loyal friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, of course, a capricious child.\NIt manifests in the most diverse forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get to know them better, the machines repay your tender attitude with a big bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, nothing else excites you more. \NThink this makes for an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. An exhaustive one.\NThanks a lot for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay a little longer. \NThis time I'll surely hit my bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really gotta leave.\NIt's lunchtime already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna get some sushi?\NI haven't dined yet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm used to dining in a specific place, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Because of good cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will also give this place a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.07,Song,,0,0,10,,Oumi Main Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- I won't, I won't! No syringes, never! \N- Hiroshi, don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, stopped crying already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! The Young Doctor said they will do it \Nthe special, totally painless way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't that relieving? \NThank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this special way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical confidentiality. \NI cannot tell you this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off! Please buckle your seatbelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a natural and ingenious form. \NAn elegant color scheme! She is beautiful in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope someday someone \Nwould praise my coffee this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I check her from the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's your heart set, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only appearance, but insides are beautiful as well. \NThis is, without a doubt, a perfect machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, you shouldn't jump to such conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This was no flattery, \Nbut my sincere opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, I hope you won't solicit her \Nfor your collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true I liked her so much \NI would've moved heaven and earth to obtain her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She is among a few astonishing machines \Nthat one sees once in a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I see these children \Nare happy to remain in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These children?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To remain in a place like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They are appreciated here by master and the playing \Npachislot guests. It makes them shine even brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have no right \Nto deprive them of such happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I never regretted going here with you today.\NNot only that I met a breathtaking machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I also had a delicious curry \Nand a fine coffee after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget riding my bike for free.\NOumi, modesty is certainly not your forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,People call such things a friendship.\NYou should try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How's work, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, let me lend you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, what's got into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. You're exhausted from work.\NPlease rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible. Those proportions! Not a single machine \Ncan even get close to being so ideal. Perfect forms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I saw these eyes' glow, \NI knew right away this is a Premium Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just hear the angel's whisper? This divine sound made my love burn with renewed vigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi Shunichi...\NA future heir to the Oumi Main Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So it entails... what? \NWhy is he grabbing my hands talking nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible purity... \NThis is the first time I meet a woman like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know my feelings are sincere! \NRight now, my flag waves towards you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.89,Song,,0,0,10,,A hanged flag = increased chance of good combinations
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! \NI got you, now please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... If you hang out with freaks, \Nbe so kind as to put them away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the details \Nof who has the flag hard for whom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your bag! Yuri... Yuri!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?\NNever have I saw her so annoyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she master's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:13:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense! They're not even a bit alike. \NInstead, would you care to explain what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... thought...\NHow do I explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, why don't we call it a day \Nand head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We are leaving!\NMaster, put it on my tab!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual.\NBe sure to come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they gone yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this guy was thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, he had in mind \Nsome odd combination with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is! Slothium's invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Member's tournament, the third round's \Ndate and time have been determined. Friday this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what opponent will I face this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bienvenue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you, Yuri!\NHaving a morning set?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.63,Song,,0,0,10,,Flag, hanged at morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Whichever that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, for how long are you going to play resentful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in any way resentful, can't you see? \NI'm very much content.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get over it! \NYou'll see, next time I'm keeping my promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too light-headed for such promises. \NBut whatever. This time I'll believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... The title is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bienvenue...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning...{\i0} I came with a present for you, \N{\i1}my sweet honey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too hasty with such decisions!\NYou know each other for less than a day may I remind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,True love cares not for the time passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi... I don't claim to be an expert, \Nbut shouldn't a doctor conduct a thorough examination
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,prior to cutting the patient's abdominal with a scalpel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for our situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Before proposing, a few important steps are required. \NYuri still knows nothing about you, not a single trait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood.\NYuri, please forget that I ever proposed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, until Yuri wants it herself, \NI'll look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how about we drink together? I know a fine place. \NWe'll enjoy a night city scenery with wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if it's just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Lil' Gin will make our third.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lil' Gin, huh? I'm getting a -chan suffix on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are three of us, I might agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Lil' Gin! My fair Ginya, Mister Ginya! \NWill you be the third one drinking with me and Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but when?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will only be free on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Friday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate... I have an important training operation appointed on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have... the manuscript deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, \NI guess no one's going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial score is 200 points.\NThe first player to score 2000 points, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Players take seats in front of machines of their choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I can show you today. \NMachines really can talk to you if you listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be only one winner.\NI look forward to ascertaining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I'm losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting in 5 seconds. 4... 3... 2... 1... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, grant me luck. I will examine your condition \Nthoroughly. I feel that you wanna grant me luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy? \NA weirdo one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is his strategy?\N- That guy is talking to his machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- He thinks it can hear him?\N- Did you bet on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bars again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NHaven't you caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get sick, I'm the man of an hour. \NI'm the one with whom you can share everything. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, remain still. \NLet me finally hear your pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No swelling.\NThe throat seems fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell do you keep murmuring there?\NI can't get my concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. \NYou definitely don't have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, isn't he a doctor?\NMeaning he is doing the palpation there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Touching the machines \Nis not prohibited, so why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi, today you look a whole different person \Ncompared to the day you played with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there is still one fatal flaw in your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have volvulus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll regret spending coins recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the doctor is bound for home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless he aims to be \Nthe premiere loser, he oughta stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure. \NEven red-only-seeking Otonashi has more chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your game looks mediocre.\NIt's still too filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a good child...\NJust marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! \NThe doctor suddenly hit Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet. \NYou shouldn't be selfish playing alone all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us enjoy the game together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the bonus strategy is in use again. \NDo you think it might just work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi's score rises slower than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,While the doctor guy scoring rapidly with a Renchan of three Bigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you outrun him with time?\NThis is growing interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. It's alright now. \NNothing will hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? I had to bust my ass this whole time \Nto somehow score these 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Oumi has almost bonus-caught-up with me. \NAm I gonna lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Small Factor is okay...\NI want a Small Factor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. You're in great shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We may see the tables turned at the last minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't score another 15, I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor's Regular bonus is over.\NWho will hit the Small Factor first?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's scissors now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a little carried away with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:36.83,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8}Game is concluded. Otonashi Ginya is the winner of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I made sure you are perfectly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, pachislot is a living being.\NI saw it myself just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out you are a Slothium member as well. \NToday's game was a great pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I won't lose.\NSee you again, Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got lucky this time.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The supple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The pianist. Teresa Sam N'Kota{no fucking clue what this name is}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NMelody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will\Nstop the time.
